---
title: Southern Beef Rump & Mustard Sauce with Sour Cream & Onion Mash
description: Long after you finish this dinner of steak and three veg, you're going to remember the way it was transformed by the simple addition of a luscious mustard sauce. It's an easy trick that gives this classic dish a new lease of life.

*Keep an eye out...Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
